The auto pricing website is mainly designed for the purpose of downloading the updated prices from the server directly.

#LINK1
http://peach-stores.ddns.net/blumaple/imports/auto_pricing.php

#LINK2 (for local network users)
192.168.1.17/blumaple/imports/auto_pricing.php

#Features of website
1.this website allows the user to download the whole inventory prices with seconds along with calculated MRP, SALE PRICE, BUSINESS PRICE, MINIMUNM & MAXIMUM PRICES.
2.It has inbuilt feature of editable cells that helps the user to make manual changes and the cells will be automatically updated with the updated prices and profit values.
3.Each individual consists of a refresh button to refresh the current prices in the website.

#Backend
1.The website works with the php scripts that on the server side while running with visual html,css and javascript.
